{"tid":744713,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚9點9 ViuTV 99   Good Night Show 全民造星   2018-07-16","createTime":"2018-07-16T06:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T15:27:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e84e2737d9cd9cbcd2459b4fd53df5808efa7167","tid":744713,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:55:54.000Z","msg":"今晚9點9 ViuTV 99  2018-07-16<br />\n<br />\nGood Night Show 全民造星<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.viu.tv/resized-512/shares/vod_images/vi_voddrama_series_desc_t/201807/zh_tw/original_horizontal/s201807150064284.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.viu.tv%2Fresized-512%2Fshares%2Fvod_images%2Fvi_voddrama_series_desc_t%2F201807%2Fzh_tw%2Foriginal_horizontal%2Fs201807150064284.jpg&h=3d292e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nViu TV 作為香港人的電視台，有使命培育新一代超級偶像，在2018年將進行一項前所未有的大型造星工程，與多個媒體合作，培育屬於香港的新星，貢獻香港娛樂圈。這項造星工程將持續3個月， 100位型男將經過首輪淘汰後再由10位星級導師，進行一系列特訓！ <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">比賽由7月16日起至10月5日，逢星期一至五</span></span>，一連60集，100型男在觀眾注視下接受不同類型歌舞及演藝比試，由各媒體代表汰弱留強，出綫選手有機會到美國接受特訓，最終一位偶像終極誕生，奪得100萬港幣獎金，成就造星傳記。"},{"pid":"4470912b64bfd6a3cc8f010ff1716e7bb314d34c","tid":744713,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T08:42:55.000Z","msg":"9.9 ViuTV 99"},{"pid":"b19393eef970725213b2d618f9e59d739cfe2ab0","tid":744713,"uid":127057,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/170407_827c0020c07b72aee81bc2d58585aba3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F170407_827c0020c07b72aee81bc2d58585aba3.png&h=626ccc1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁醜樣退出都岩<br />\n琴日睇前傳 人又乸 又自大<br />\n唔係咁既樣諗住做巨星丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 佢好似係家燕媽得意門生"},{"pid":"e8c43584378f1f86626c